14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 50 O.S. 2021, Section 21, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 21. The repeated use of any real property or structure
18 thereon to commit unlawful drug distribution, prostitution, or human
19 and/or sex trafficking acts which result in a felony conviction
20 under the Oklahoma Uniform Controlled Dangerous Substances Act may
21 shall constitute a public nuisance.
22 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
